org.lobobrowser.html.w3c

Interface HTMLIFrameElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.w3c.dom.Element, HTMLElement, org.w3c.dom.Node
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HTMLIFrameElementImpl

    public interface HTMLIFrameElement
extends HTMLElement
    Inline subwindows. See the IFRAME element definition in HTML 4.01.

    See also the Object Model (DOM) Level 2 HTML Specification

    .
